      "comment" : "Button label for rescanning places.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "You'll see a quick preview right away. The album is then fully analyzed and refined while your iPhone is locked, charging, and connected to Wi-Fi (typically overnight) — results improve automatically as photos are indexed." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
